==English==
=== Noun ===
'''aegis'''
# Friendly protection, guidance, or control.   
#* Usually as `''under the aegis''' because of its origin as protection of the shield of [[:w:Athena|Athena]].
# Mythological shield associated with Zeus and Athena shown as a short cloak consisting of a goatskin with a border of snakes and with the head of Medusa in the center - more an emblem of protection and power than an actual military shield.

